  "stac_version": "1.1.0",
  "description": "This dataset provides annual summaries of fractional land cover derived from Landsat imagery across the Pacific region. It aggregates scene-based observations into yearly statistical measures such as percentiles and counts of valid observations. The dataset supports long-term environmental monitoring, trend analysis, and land-use change assessment.\n\nLineage:\nGenerated by aggregating Landsat fractional cover observations into annual statistical summaries.\n\nProcessing level:\nSummary / Statistical Product\n\nDataset type:\nAnnual time series",
